这篇论文是我更广泛的创作宇宙的一部分，与我的小说《奥德赛2999》和神学随笔《归乡》共享同一哲学根基：恩典拓扑主义。但论文本身是自足的，可以独立阅读。

This paper is part of a broader creative universe, sharing philosophical foundations with my novel Odyssey 2999 and theological essay Exhelldus: Grace Topology. However, the paper stands alone and can be read independently.

Soli Deo Gloria.
愿一切荣耀归给独一真神。
